- cs.OS (Operating Systems) is a possible category because the paper mentions that signaling is provided by many operating systems. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category because the paper introduces a flexible abstraction for memory reclamation schemes. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category because the paper discusses modularity and ease of interchangeability of memory reclamation schemes.
